---
title: Carb Smart Bacon Taco Salad with Chipotle Crema and Charred Corn
description: This easy salad packs in flavour and a ton of protein from eggs, bacon and cheese. Lime and bacon fat are the base of this zesty dressing and we top it all off with a zippy chipotle sour cream drizzle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/carb-smart-bacon-taco-salad-fb3d38ff.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/carb-smart-bacon-taco-salad-648827518b7cbe6ce106c885-2531d158.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipes/carb-smart-bacon-taco-salad-648827518b7cbe6ce106c885
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: Latin
course: main course
nutrition:
  calories: 600 kcal
